        <section eId="sec_59_1_612">
          <num>59-1-612</num>
          <heading>Formal hearing to exhaust administrative remedies.</heading>
          <content>
            <p>Effective 5/14/2019
59-1-612.
Formal hearing to exhaust administrative remedies.
A party has not exhausted the party's administrative remedies in accordance with Section
63G-4-401
unless:
(1)
the party requests a formal hearing within the time period provided by law; and
(2)
the commission has issued a final unappealable administrative order.
Enacted by Chapter
351
, 2019 General Session</p>
          </content>
          <subsection eId="59_1_612__subsec_1">
            <num>(1)</num>
            <content>
              <p>the party requests a formal hearing within the time period provided by law; and</p>
            </content>
          </subsection>
          <subsection eId="59_1_612__subsec_2">
            <num>(2)</num>
            <content>
              <p>the commission has issued a final unappealable administrative order.</p>
            </content>
          </subsection>
        </section>
      </chapter>
